<%- include('partials/header') -%>

Show one specific lesson and let you edit like save copy and more.


<div id="copyMe">
        <h2>Title: <%=lesson.bookTitle%></h2>
        <h4>Author: <%=lesson.bookAuthor%></h4>
        <h4>Skill: <%=lesson.vocabSkill%></h4>
        <h4>Lesson Introduction: <%=lesson.lessonIntro%></h4>
        <h4>Journal Activity: <%=lesson.lessonActivity%></h4>
</div>

<a href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=<%=lesson.bookTitle%>"><i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i>Search this book on Youtube</a>

<button onclick="copyDivToClipboard()">Copy Lesson to Clipboard</button>
<span>Thanks <b><%=author.userName%></b> for sharing this lesson.</span>

<!-- 
     user Id  <%=lesson.user%>
